'''古物奇谭'''是一个半小时的[[纪录片|纪录片]]/[[真人秀|真人秀]]型电视节目，讲的是在一家位于[[东村_(纽约市)|纽约东村]]专门买卖古物和其他稀有物品的古物杂货店是怎样经营的。2010年11月4日节目在[[探索频道|探索频道]]和姊妹频道[[科学频道|科学频道]]首播。<ref name="aol">{{en}}{{Cite web  | last = Muessig  | first = Ben  | title = From Skulls to Straitjackets, This Is Your One-Stop Shop  | publisher = AOL News  | date = November 2, 201  | url = http://www.aolnews.com/2010/11/02/from-skulls-to-straightjackets-this-shop-is-your-one-stop-shop/  | accessdate = 1-3-11  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213201710/http://www.aolnews.com/2010/11/02/from-skulls-to-straightjackets-this-shop-is-your-one-stop-shop/  | archivedate = 2012-02-13  }}</ref><ref name="starr">{{en}}{{Cite web  | last = Starr  | first = Michael  | title = Starr Report  | work = New York Post  | date = October 25, 2010  | url = http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/starr_report_SLRCTGzkKidBL7VrYkmUuK  | accessdate = 1-3-11  | archive-date = 2012-10-21  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021183639/http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/starr_report_SLRCTGzkKidBL7VrYkmUuK  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

古物奇谭的重点在于每天对古物和古怪物品的经营，店铺的共同拥有者麦克·佐恩和伊凡·迈克尔逊以及买手赖恩·马修维持着日常经营，迎接来访的各色顾客。<ref name="bios">{{en}}{{Cite web  | title = Meet the Team: Obscura Antiques & Oddities  | work = Oddities  | publisher = Discovery Communications  | date = 2011  | url = http://dsc.discovery.com/tv/oddities/bios.html  | accessdate = 1-3-11  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101120053140/http://dsc.discovery.com/tv/oddities/bios.html  | archivedate = 2010-11-20  }}</ref>店铺的员工会从跳蚤市场、个人收藏、拍卖和古董展中搜寻独一无二的和不寻常的古物。节目的主要内容就是古物的买卖，包括[[木乃伊|木乃伊]]猫、[[普通猕猴|猕猴]]头骨、指甲艺术品、[[拘束衣|拘束衣]]等。<ref name="starr"/><ref name="discblog">{{en}}{{Cite web  | first = G.  | last = Weiswasser  | title = The Odd World of 'Oddities' on Discovery Channel  | work = DiscoveryBlog  | publisher = Discovery Communications  | date = November 3, 2010  | url = http://corporate.discovery.com/blog/2010/11/03/the-odd-world-of-oddities-on-discovery-channel/  | accessdate = 1-3-11  | archive-date = 2010-12-28  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101228020704/http://corporate.discovery.com/blog/2010/11/03/the-odd-world-of-oddities-on-discovery-channel/  | dead-url = no  }}</ref><ref name="nymag">{{en}}{{Cite journal  | last = Salazar  | first = Lauren  | title = Obscura Antiques and Oddities  | journal = New York Magazine  | publisher = New York Media  | url = http://nymag.com/listings/stores/obscura-antiques-and-oddities/  | accessdate = 1-3-11  | archive-date = 2018-11-19  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181119011930/http://nymag.com/listings/stores/obscura-antiques-and-oddities/  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

节目中出现的名人包括[[科恩乐队|科恩乐队]]的主唱{{Link-en|乔纳森·戴维斯|Jonathan Davis}}；{{Link-en|Stiffs, Inc.|Stiffs, Inc.}}的主唱惠特尼·斯特林；演员[[马修·葛雷·古博勒|马修·葛雷·古博勒]]；喜剧演员{{Link-en|艾米·塞达里斯|Amy Sedaris}}；女演员[[科洛·塞维尼|科洛·塞维尼]]；电子游戏设计师和商业太空飞行爱好者[[理查·盖瑞特|理查·盖瑞特]]；导演[[劳埃德·考夫曼|劳埃德·考夫曼]]；微核说唱歌手{{Link-en|沙弗·黑暗领主|Schäffer the Darklord}}等。

